Your Honor,

I stand before you today to express my sincere remorse and to respectfully plead guilty to the charge of careless driving. I fully accept responsibility for my actions and acknowledge the gravity of my offense, understanding the potential consequences.

On the day of the incident, I deeply regret my behavior as I was rushing to the airport to pick up my family members. In my haste, I made poor choices, driving aggressively, exceeding the speed limit, and even engaging with my cellphone while behind the wheel. These reckless decisions led to a collision with a guardrail, causing damage and endangering the safety of others. I am truly sorry for my actions.

